Developer Terms of Use
des: Golfers can now check for available tee times up to 7 days in advance using an Amazon Alexa device or the Amazon Alexa phone app. Through this easily accessible voice assistant, courses will reduce the amount of incoming calls into the pro shop and help practice social distancing. If you would like create an Amazon Alexa voice assistant for your course, send us an email at voiceITgolf@gmail.com.
